    "en": {
      "title": "The Philippines is rocked by an earthquake",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "An earthquake with a magnitude of 7.1 on the Richter scale shook the island of Luzon in the northern part of the Philippines.",
        "Philippine media reports said four people died and 60 were injured in the earthquake. Many houses and buildings were destroyed by the earthquake.",
        "The earthquake occurred on the sea floor 11 kilometers off the town of Dolores.",
        "The number of buildings damaged by the earthquake is 108. The number of houses destroyed due to landslides is 58."
      ],
